Monitorix - ChangeLog
=====================

	Changed: Run cronjob with lower priority

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.2.2
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Fixed: The plugin's data are not available when plugin is loaded through a cron job
	Fixed: #IP-1419 Monitorix: Missing bin_path configuration parameter
	Fixed: Syntax error in cronjob file

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.2.1
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Updated: Dutch language file

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.2.0
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Removed: Support for i-MSCP 1.1.x serie

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.1.2
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Fixed: Wrong name passed to the iMSCP_Plugin_Manager::getPluginInfo() method

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.1.1
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Added: Missing cgi directory ( relative to the base_dir directory )
	Disabled: Graphs which require further configuration to be enabled
	Fixed: Wrong graph names inserted into extra configuration file ( 20-imscp.conf )

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.1.0
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Added: Dedicated monitorix configuration file ( Good practice )
	Added: bin_path, cgi_path and confdir_path configuration parameters ( Good practice )
	Added: Localization support
	Changed: Monitorix cronjob is now run every 30 minutes
	Changed: The default monitorix configuration file is now left untouched ( Good practice )
	Fixed: Graphs must not be loaded through PHP ( Performance issue )
	Fixed: Monitorix CGI script must be left untouched ( Good practice )
	Fixed: Plugin is not compatible with i-MSCP 1.2.x
	Fixed: Unable to restart monitorix ( umask issue - fixed in i-MSCP Core )

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.0.0
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Fixed: Disable internal httpd daemon of Monitorix

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.9
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Fixed: Backend file path in cronjob
	Fixed: Unable to connect to MySQL

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.8
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Fixed: Monitorix CGI binary must be run indirectly for partitions which are mounted with the noexec option

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.7
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Fixed: Cronjob file path

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.6
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Fixed: Path to monitorix.conf
	Fixed: Url for graphics creation
	Added: New parameter in config.php to enable graphs

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.5
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Fixed: Plugin is not compatible with monitorix 3.5.0

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.4
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Fixed: Plugin is not compatible with Perl version from Squeeze

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.3
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Updated according new plugin API (0.2.4)

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.2
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Updated according new plugin API (0.2.0)

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.1
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	First Release
